    "text": "On the evening of 02.04.2026, acting on intelligence received by officers of the Computer Crime Investigation Division of the Criminal Investigation Department, a raid was conducted at a hotel in the Iranawila area within the Chilaw Police Division. During the operation, 152 foreign nationals including 137 Chinese citizens were apprehended on suspicion of engaging in online financial fraud.",
