    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      574.77,
      526.4,
      629.45
    ],
    "text": "Equipment believed to have been used in the commission of these offences, including 177 computers and approximately 577 mobile phones, was seized and taken into the custody of the investigating officers. Preliminary investigations have revealed that the suspects had been carrying out these fraudulent activities at the said hotel for a period of nearly two months.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
